snippet.textDisplay: When I was younger I used to dye my naturally brown hair with coffee (on the ends that would get sun bleached).  But what I would do is create a coffee reduction on the stove (many cups of espresso then boil for some time).  I let it cool and then "steep" my hair for a couple of hours.  It worked but washed out in about 2 weeks...
